--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Description of Beam parameters
The file is read by invoking UI command /G4M/Beam/file.
The parameters are set to G4MBeamGun at G4MBeamGunMessenger.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
150                    ;  Beam ID       [ not used for setting. ]
proton 150 MeV         ;  Description   [ not used for setting. ]
2212                   ;  Particle ID
150.05  0.00           ;  Beam Energy [MeV],   Beam Energy Spread [MeV]
0.0     0.0            ;  Angular variance,Spatial covariance [ not used]
2.16    2.16           ;  Spatial variance in X, and in Y [mm]
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------


